version_description:
We're constantly working to improve your mobile banking experience!

This update includes:
• UI Improvements
• SecureSwipe - Take control by locking and unlocking your Debit Card.
• PicturePay - Take pictures of your bills and let us do the work for you.
• FSCB Mobile Banking is now available on Apple Watch
